'''CrossGaming''' is an esports organization based in Hong Kong. All the athletes of CrossGaming are amateur. The team was first formed to compete in [[IEM Season VI - Global Challenge Guangzhou|IEM Guangzhou]], and went through a series of lineup changes after the event.

